    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK188">
<l>tuṉṉiyār kuṟṟamun tūṟṟu marapiṉā</l>
<l>reṉṉaiko letilār māṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What will those not do to strangers whose nature leads them to publish abroad the faults of their intimate friends ?</l>
